---
title: Oven-Baked Steak with Roasted Veggies and Parmesan Mash
description: This steak will be perfectly juicy and tender after searing each side and just a few minutes in the oven. Roasting the vegetables with the steak make this dish extra easy and fabulous. Look out for this Parmesan mash too; it’s an absolute winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/oven-baked-steak-fe297578.jpg
